        "content": "## 🛡️ Check Point Documentation\n#### AI Agent over MCP · via Gateway\n\nSearches official Check Point docs and SecureKnowledge — answers with citations.\n\n**How it works:** Every call rides the **Docker MCP Gateway** — one endpoint, Bearer auth, the whole Check Point MCP fleet behind it.\n\n**💬 Try these:**\n- How do I enable Identity Awareness on R82?\n- Find the SK about the Gaia API\n\n**🧠 Models:** Azure OpenAI `gpt-5.4` is wired as default — swap by connecting Ollama (local, no key), Gemini, OpenAI or Claude to the *Chat Model* port.",
